title: Watch The Latest Trailer For ‘Wonder Woman’ Here
text:
✨Welcome to Themyscria. I am proud to present the NEW trailer for #WonderWoman ! ✨ pic.twitter.com/7q7SQ80ut1 
— Gal Gadot (@GalGadot) March 12, 2017 
Warner Bros. teased a new Wonder Woman for Saturday, making fans check in throughout the day for the possible release. Well finally it has arrived, but was it worth the wait? 
(Via Warner Brothers)
